OL,6,FTributes have been paid to two men who
OL,7,Fwere killed in a crash between a car
OL,8,Fand a lorry in the Vale of Glamorgan.
OL,10,FThree men died after the crash on the
OL,11,FA48 near Bonvilston shortly before 5pm
OL,12,Fon Tuesday, 1 April.
OL,14,FPolice have named two of the men as
OL,15,FLawrence Howells, 51, from Porthcawl,
OL,16,Fand Barrie John, 48, from Ferndale,
OL,17,FRhondda.
