OL,6,FIn a tribute, Mr Howells' family said:
OL,7,F"As a family we are devastated and ask
OL,8,Ffor time to grieve and process the
OL,9,Floss of Lawrence. Sleep tight Law boy.
OL,10,FOur thoughts also go out to other
OL,11,Ffamilies affected by this tragic
OL,12,Faccident."
OL,14,FA tribute released by the family of
OL,15,FBarrie John said: "He brought so much
OL,16,Flife and laughter into everything. His
OL,17,Fenergy was contagious. He was always
OL,18,Fcracking jokes, pulling pranks. Now,
OL,19,Fhe's gone, and the silence is
OL,20,Fdeafening.
