OL,6,F"Though the sorrow is overwhelming,
OL,7,Fthere's still a flicker of hope that
OL,8,Fhis spirit lives on in the love and
OL,9,Fmemories we hold."
OL,11,FBarrie's sister Donna said: "I can't
OL,12,Fput in words just how broken I'm
OL,13,Ffeeling right now knowing that I'm
OL,14,Fnever going to see you or hear your
OL,15,Fvoice again with our goofy ways, but I
OL,16,Fwill never forget our memories with
OL,17,FNigel, your nieces and nephew and the
OL,18,Fway you made us all laugh. I love you
OL,19,Falways your baby sister, Donna."
